SELECT
  avg(individuals."ACE_swore_at_or_put_down" + individuals."ACE_pushed_shoved_grabbed_slapped" + individuals."ACE_sexually_abused" + 
  individuals."ACE_unloved" + individuals."ACE_uncared_for" + individuals."ACE_broken_home" + individuals."ACE_mother_pushed_shoved_grabbed_slapped" +
  individuals."ACE_lived_with_addict" + individuals."ACE_household_member_mentally_ill" + individuals."ACE_household_member_went_to_prison") as "ACE Score"
FROM
  individuals, cohorts
WHERE
  individuals.cohort_id = cohorts.id AND cohorts.meeting_night IN ($Cohort)

SELECT
  avg(assessments.ssa_family_best_description_current_situation_housing) as "Housing"
FROM
  (SELECT
     individual_id, MIN(date_collected) AS date_collected
   FROM
     assessments
   GROUP BY
     individual_id) AS first_assessments, assessments, individuals, cohorts
WHERE
  assessments.individual_id = first_assessments.individual_id AND
  individuals.id = first_assessments.individual_id AND
  assessments.date_collected = first_assessments.date_collected AND
  individuals.cohort_id = cohorts.id AND cohorts.meeting_night IN ($Cohort)

SELECT
  cohorts.meeting_night as "Cohort", assessments.individual_id as "ID", individuals.first_name as "First Name", 
  individuals.last_name as "Last Name", assessments.ssa_family_best_description_current_situation_housing as "Housing",
  assessments.ssa_family_best_description_current_situation_transportation as "Transportation",
  assessments.ssa_primary_adult_enrolled_best_description_academic as "Education",
  assessments.ssa_family_best_description_current_situation_income as "Income",
  assessments.ssa_health_insurance as "H Ins.",
  assessments.ssa_medical_physical_family_member_impact as "Phys H",
  assessments.ssa_family_best_description_current_situation_mental_health as "Mental H",
  assessments.ssa_primary_adult_enrolled_best_description_stressors as "Environ",
  assessments.ssa_primary_adult_enrolled_parenting as "Parenting",
  assessments.ssa_quality_childcare as "Childcare",
  assessments.ssa_criminal as "Legal / Crim",
  assessments.ssa_legal_non_criminal as "Legal / Non-Crim",
  assessments.ssa_support_system as "Support System",
  assessments.ssa_food as "Food",
  assessments.ssa_home_safety as "Home Safety",
  assessments.ssa_community_involvement as "Community Involvement"
FROM
  (SELECT
     individual_id, MIN(date_collected) AS date_collected
   FROM
     assessments
   GROUP BY
     individual_id) AS latest_assessments, assessments, individuals, cohorts
WHERE
  assessments.individual_id = latest_assessments.individual_id AND
  assessments.date_collected = latest_assessments.date_collected AND
  individuals.cohort_id = cohorts.id AND cohorts.meeting_night IN ($Cohort)
ORDER BY
  cohorts.meeting_night, assessments.individual_id asc

SELECT
  avg(assessments.credit_score) as "Credit Score"
FROM
  (SELECT
     individual_id, MIN(date_collected) AS date_collected
   FROM
     assessments
   GROUP BY
     individual_id) AS first_assessments, assessments, individuals, cohorts
WHERE
  assessments.individual_id = first_assessments.individual_id AND
  individuals.id = first_assessments.individual_id AND
  assessments.date_collected = first_assessments.date_collected AND
  individuals.cohort_id = cohorts.id AND cohorts.meeting_night IN ($Cohort) AND
  assessments.credit_score > 0
